Input cases:

 Output cases:
 Case1: 1 real

 Case4: 1 virtual
 Example use cases with asset mappings
 1 1: Swapping.

 1 4: Opening lending position OR Purchasing NFT. Input real asset, get back virtual asset representing NFT or position.
